      "name": "Product Info",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "header_type": "left",
        "heading": "<h2>Built for Chefs on the Move</h2>",
        "content": "<p>Whether you're commuting to work, heading to a cooking class, or travelling with your collection — a quality knife roll protects your edges, organises your tools, and looks outstanding doing it.</p>",
