        "footer_type": "third",
        "footer_left": "<p>We don't do cheap accessories. The same commitment to premium materials and craftsmanship that goes into every Xinzuo blade goes into every roll, strap, and buckle.</p>",
        "footer_right": "<p>30-day returns, Australian-owned, and backed by Australian Consumer Law.</p>",
